znew=read.table("~/Dropbox/summaryZ.mpn_chip_dnmt3a_tet2.tsv.gz",sep="\t",header=T)

a=do.call(rbind, strsplit(znew$SNPID, ':'))
chr=a[,1]
a2=do.call(rbind, strsplit(chr, 'chr'))
chr=a2[,2]

bp=do.call(rbind, strsplit(a[,2], '\\|'))[,1]
znew$a.chr=chr
znew$a.pos=as.numeric(as.character(bp))


bed=read.table("~/Dropbox//ld_chunk.bed")
head(bed)
maxes=apply(znew[,c(2:5)],1,function(x){max(abs(x))})

znew$maxes=maxes
bed$V1=do.call(rbind, strsplit(bed$V1, 'chr'))[,2]

max_block=data.frame(matrix(ncol = ncol(znew), nrow = nrow(bed)))
colnames(max_block)=(colnames(znew))





for(i in 1:nrow(bed)){
  chr=bed[i,1]
  start=bed[i,2]
  stop=bed[i,3]
  in_chrom=znew[znew$a.chr==chr,]##extract those of the same
  goodguys=in_chrom[in_chrom$a.pos>start&in_chrom$a.pos<stop,]
 if(nrow(goodguys)>0) {
    z.max=which.max(goodguys[,"maxes"])
    z_good=goodguys[z.max,]
    z_good$a.chr=as.character(z_good$a.chr)
    } else {
      z_good=rep(0,ncol(max_block))
    }
  #z_good=data.table(z_good,stringsAsFactors = F)
  
  #z_good$=rownames(goodguys)[z.max]
  max_block[i,]=z_good
  print(i)
}

max_block=na.omit(max_block)

saveRDS(max_block,"~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/chip_mash_max_block.rds")
source('~/Dropbox/mash_materials/flashscript.R')
zmash=as.matrix(znew[c(2:5)])
rownames(zmash)=znew$SNPID
#zmash=readRDS("~/Dropbox/cadproject/zmash_mat.rds")
# identify a random subset of 20000 tests
random.subset = sample(1:nrow(zmash),40000)
data.temp = mash_set_data(zmash[random.subset,],alpha = 1)
Vhat = estimate_null_correlation_simple(data.temp)##correlation matrix of the errors
saveRDS(Vhat,"~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/Vhat.rds")
library("lattice")
clrs = colorRampPalette((c("#D73027","#FC8D59","#FEE090","#FFFFBF", "#E0F3F8","#91BFDB","#4575B4")))(64)

print(levelplot(Vhat,col.regions = clrs,xlab = "",ylab = "",colorkey = TRUE,main="VHAT"))

rm(data.temp)
data.random = mash_set_data(zmash[random.subset,],alpha = 1,V=Vhat)##use for E(Z)model

max_block=readRDS("~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/chip_mash_max_block.rds")
zmax=apply(max_block[,c(2:5)],2,function(x){as.numeric(x)});
rownames(zmax)=max_block$SNPID
data.strong = mash_set_data(zmax,alpha = 1,V=Vhat)

U.pca = cov_pca(data.strong,3)
U.flash=cov_flash(data.strong,remove_singleton = T)
#, non_canonical = TRUE)
X.center = apply(data.strong$Bhat, 2, function(x) x - mean(x))
U.ed = cov_ed(data.strong, c(U.pca,U.flash,list("XX" = t(X.center) %*% X.center / nrow(X.center))))
saveRDS(U.ed,"~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/EDcov.Rds")

U.c = cov_canonical(data.random)

m = mash(data.random, Ulist = c(U.ed,U.c),outputlevel = 1)
saveRDS(m,"~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/mfitCHIP.rds")
saveRDS(zmash,"~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/zmash.rds")
m=readRDS("~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/mfitCHIP.rds")
zmash=readRDS("~/Dropbox/monster_mash/chip_project/zmash.rds")
k=length(m$fitted_g$Ulist)
l=length(m$fitted_g$grid)

barplot(colSums(pimat),las=2)

  p=file$PosteriorMean

}
